{"tid":1556472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[18區] 旺角moko大合唱","createTime":"2019-09-09T17:47:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T16:34:40.000Z","uid":164420,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"5f83ee2348c723ce33440c2733d22d76ca7468e4","tid":1556472,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:47:28.000Z","msg":"太古城班中產都唱左，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">MK仔女點可以落後於人</span></span>？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9月10 星期二 晚上9:00，</span></span>全體MK街坊集合moko各層一齊大合唱 &lt;願榮光歸香港&gt;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《願榮光歸香港 Glory To Hong Kong》<br />\n<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流<br />\nFor all of our tears on our land<br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨<br />\nDo you feel the rage in our cries?<br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透<br />\nRise up and speak up! Our voice echoes<br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡<br />\nFreedom shall shine upon us<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走<br />\nFor all of our fear that lingers<br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後<br />\nWith faith, we shall never surrender<br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透<br />\nWith blood, tears and sweat, we shall stride ahead<br />\n建自由 光輝 香港<br />\nFor this glory, lib-eral land<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在 晚星 墜落 徬徨 午夜<br />\nWhen the stars no longer guide our path<br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處 吹 來 號 角 聲<br />\nIn the fog, the horn of conscience summon us<br />\n&quot;捍自由 來齊集這裡 來全力抗對<br />\n&ldquo;Persevere! For we are as one, with poise and be brave<br />\n勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅&quot;<br />\nCourage, wisdom, are long with us.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港<br />\nThe dawn has come. Let&rsquo;s revive our Hong Kong<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命<br />\nRevolution of our time! For righteousness!<br />\n祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽<br />\nDemocracy, n&rsquo;liberty, wish them long last here<br />\n我願 榮光 歸香港<br />\nFor the glory of Hong Kong"},{"pid":"a5675b0950f6af7c36c48668b01f42adaceff28f","tid":1556472,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:48:00.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"1